Blackstone Family GP L.L.C: Private Company Information - Bloomberg








































  





















































































July 26, 2017 12:22 PM ET

Company Overview of Blackstone Family GP L.L.C



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Blackstone Family GP L.L.C operates as a general partner of Blackstone Family Investment Partnership (Cayman) V-SMD L.P. The company was incorporated in 2007 and is based in New York, New York.


345 Park AvenueNew York, NY 10154United StatesFounded in 2007



